</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>may require <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:How_to_copy-edit" title="Wikipedia:How to copy-edit">copy-editing</a> for grammar, style, cohesion, tone or spelling</b>. You can assist by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Supply_chain_management&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Supply_chain_management&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">editing it</a> now. A how-to <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:How_to_copy-edit" title="Wikipedia:How to copy-edit">guide</a> is available.<small><i>&#160;(October 2007)</i></small></td>
